The latest data from NetMarketShare shows that Windows 7 is still ahead of Windows 10 on PC. The April 2018 statistics showed that Android 7.0 and Android 6.0 were the most popular operating systems on mobile, with 19.25% and 15.95% market share respectively. Android 8.0 has also gained significant market share and now accounts for 8.28% of all mobile operating systems. The most popular operating systems on desktop and mobile for April 2018 are detailed below.  